Title: #001: 4 Practices to Become a Self-Aware Leader | Looking Back
Description:
What trumps education, skills, charisma, and even talent? The surprising answer: self-awareness. A study from Cornell found self-awareness to be the “strongest predictor of overall success” among top leaders. Discover why it’s so important—and how to cultivate it for yourself.
